extends layout.pug

block body
  div(class='parallax-container')
    div(class='parallax')
      img(src='/public/img/about.png')
    div(class='parallax-text')
      h1(class='center') About Us
  div(class='container')
    div(class='row')
      div(class='col s12')
        h3(class='center') Our Story
        div(class='divider')
        p(class='flow-text about-text')
          | Founded in 2016 with the intention of helping small and medium sized businesses, Emerging Corporate Capital seeks to find and finance innovative industries in the public sector with workable capital, when traditional sources of capital are unavailable. The company believes that by providing the capital needed to many of these firms, these firms will be able to access venues that otherwise would be unavailable given their status, opening up many opportunities.
    div(class='row')
      div(class='col s12')
        h3(class='center') What We Do
    div(class='row')
      div(class="col l4 s12")
        div(class="card")
          div(class="card-image")
            img(src="public/img/financing.png")
            div(class='card-title black white-text') Financing
          div(class='card-content')
            p(class='flow-text about-text')
              |Shit about financing here
      div(class="col l4 s12")
        div(class="card")
          div(class="card-image")
            img(src="public/img/crypto.jpg")
            div(class='card-title black white-text') Cryptocurrency
          div(class='card-content')
            p(class='flow-text about-text')
              |Our team has extensive expertise in cryptocurrency mining and trading as well as blockchain technology
      div(class="col l4 s12")
        div(class="card")
          div(class="card-image")
            img(src="public/img/distribution.jpg")
            div(class='card-title black white-text') Distribution
          div(class='card-content')
            p(class='flow-text about-text')
              |Shit about crypto here
